15,01The Apocalypse

15,01The mushrooms are sprouting
15,01Apocalypse at hand
15,01A bomb has been dropped
15,01Out over the land

15,01Theres nowhere to run
15,01Theres nowhere to hide
15,01Death will find you
15,01And give you a ride

15,01People are screaming
15,01I wish I was dreaming
15,01The land it is glowing
15,01Death overflowing

15,01Buildings are falling
15,01Children are calling
15,01Flesh: It is burning
15,01My stomach is churning

15,01Nuclear fallout
15,01Radiation supreme
15,01I cannot escape
15,01This horrible dream

15,01The world is ending
15,01Chaos decending
15,01The future is dim
15,01Our destiny grim

15,01So in the end
15,01Everything lost
15,01Mankind has paid
15,01The ultimate cost

15,01Poem by Liquidator of Revolt Literary
